Account - Class in vamartid.test1._email
This class Account Each Account object has a username a password a First name, a Last name ,a birthday and a current Address Account objects are used both from the client and the server
Account(String, String, String, String, String, String) - Constructor for class vamartid.test1._email.Account
This method Account is the constructor of the Account objects and it just gives the given values to the object's Strings
Account(Account) - Constructor for class vamartid.test1._email.Account
